{"type": "article", "id": 27662, "title": "三角形扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-02T07:27:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145753Gxsy9zFYQ4uI5Mmp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>哪怕房间小也不用愁听不到好音乐了，Julien Tupula 专门为小户型设计了一款高保真扬声器 Nepsu Triangle。除了常规的摆放方式外，三角形的设计使它同样适用于房间的角落或是悬挂在墙壁上。未来 Tupula 还会推出一些墙面装饰，与 Triangle 配套使用可以打造不同的家居风格。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/nepsu-triangle-the-most-convenient-hi-fi-speaker#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 209 美元，而且它的多个部件都支持定制。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145750qUijB02pKuSowftO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145751xQ3HuL6tmkdYEXwv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145752nXM8SGYwDOmTljq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145752wMjJzONml71dA9ki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}